### Running Tests
This project uses pytest for testing. To run the tests:

```bash
# Install test dependencies
pip install -e ".[test]"

# Run all tests
pytest

# Run with coverage report
pytest --cov=emdb --cov-report=html

# Run specific test file
pytest tests/test_client.py
```

